  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Blue-Eyes Toon Ultimate Dragon",
      "effect": "\"Blue-Eyes Toon Dragon\" + 2 Toon monsters\nMust be Special Summoned (from your Extra Deck) by shuffling the above cards from your hand, field, and/or GY into the Deck/Extra Deck. Your Toon monsters can attack directly. Once per turn: You can add 1 \"Toon\" card, or 1 card that mentions a \"Toon\" card's name, from your GY to your hand. During damage calculation, if your Toon monster is attacked: You can banish it until the end of the Damage Step.",
      "official": false
    },
    "ja": {
      "name": "\u30d6\u30eb\u30fc\u30a2\u30a4\u30ba\u30fb\u30c8\u30a5\u30fc\u30f3\u30fb\u30a2\u30eb\u30c6\u30a3\u30e1\u30c3\u30c8\u30c9\u30e9\u30b4\u30f3",
